The film opens with Clare arriving in Berlin,&nbsp;
Germany, as a young female tourist. She walks&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:23.760 --> 00:00:28.560
to her accommodation, a hostel with group&nbsp;
bunking rooms and spends the evening partying&nbsp;&nbsp;

