upstairs apartment is tucked away behind a locked&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:01:42.800 --> 00:01:47.200
building foyer, through a small enclosed&nbsp;
courtyard into the building block behind.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:01:47.200 --> 00:01:50.640
They spend the night and she talks&nbsp;
about how much she'd like to stay&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:01:50.640 --> 00:01:55.360
rather than move onto her next destination&nbsp;
Dusseldorf. In the morning he leaves for work,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:01:55.360 --> 00:02:00.965
teaching at a local school. One student, Franka&nbsp;
details a book the class was asked to read.

