couldn't leave and he realises he forgot&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:02:23.520 --> 00:02:28.480
to leave a key for her which he finds in his&nbsp;
pocket. She jokingly suggests "did you lock me&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:02:28.480 --> 00:02:33.280
in?" and he playfully replies "yes sure, but&nbsp;
