00:02:33.280 --> 00:02:38.560
have meat injection game in the shower. They&nbsp;
go out clubbing and she stays a second night.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:02:38.560 --> 00:02:42.800
In the morning when he leaves for work he points&nbsp;
out the key he's left for her on the dresser.

00:02:45.360 --> 00:02:50.080
She casually pokes around the apartment while&nbsp;
cooking herself breakfast and finds the book of&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:02:50.080 --> 00:02:55.280
artworks from the bookshop. She opens it to her&nbsp;
favorite page and finds a photo of her asleep&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:02:55.280 --> 00:03:00.960
with the word 'mine' written on her shoulder,&nbsp;
resting in the pages. Bothered by this she also&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:00.960 --> 00:03:05.200
realises her necklace with her ring is missing.&nbsp;
Her mother had given her the ring to "hock and&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:05.200 --> 00:03:11.280
return home if she gets into trouble" but it also&nbsp;
has sentimental value. She searches the apartment&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:11.280 --> 00:03:16.560
and begins to panic, discovering the key won't&nbsp;
open the door, her mobile phone has no service,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:16.560 --> 00:03:21.920
the other internal door is also locked, and none&nbsp;
