00:03:21.920 --> 00:03:26.925
now she tries to break the window with a chair&nbsp;
and finds a second, reinforced panel behind.

00:03:29.440 --> 00:03:35.360
When Andi returns she's waiting at the door and&nbsp;
asks to leave but he won't let her past. He locks&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:35.360 --> 00:03:40.080
the door and confronts her about the broken&nbsp;
window, telling her casually if she tries to&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:40.080 --> 00:03:44.880
break the window he will have to border them up.&nbsp;
Now understanding the weight of the situation she&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:44.880 --> 00:03:50.240
pleads for him to let her go but he dismisses her&nbsp;
concerns and hands her flowers and asks if she&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:50.240 --> 00:03:55.920
likes pasta. Frustrated at his insanity she bursts&nbsp;
violently into a rage trying to kick and punch&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:55.920 --> 00:04:00.800
him but he subdues her and ties her to the bed&nbsp;
explaining that no one can hear her screams, the&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:04:00.800 --> 00:04:05.840
buildings are abandoned. The camera pans out to&nbsp;
reveal her screams are not heard from the street.

00:04:08.400 --> 00:04:12.480
The following day Andi visits his&nbsp;
father who asks why he was late.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:04:12.480 --> 00:04:17.680
Andi says he met someone and tells him&nbsp;
about Clare. His father asks about Natalie,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:04:17.680 --> 00:04:21.461
the girl he has been seeing and Andi&nbsp;
tells him she returned to Canada.

00:04:23.600 --> 00:04:28.320
Andi returns to the apartment where he has&nbsp;
continued to tie Clare to the bed on a plastic&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:04:28.320 --> 00:04:33.520
sheet. She is untied for a shower as she has&nbsp;
urinated on herself, and finds clumps of long&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:04:33.520 --> 00:04:38.400
blonde hair in the drain, realising there has&nbsp;
