00:04:38.400 --> 00:04:43.520
a puzzle and enthusiastically tells her, he told&nbsp;
his father about her and has texted her Mum that&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:04:43.520 --> 00:04:48.960
she is okay. Clare threatens that her mum will&nbsp;
