a lock-box and leave it on a shelf in the&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:00.880 --> 00:05:06.560
building corridor. Clare searches the apartment,&nbsp;
finding a screwdriver under the couch. At work,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:06.560 --> 00:05:10.240
Andi is annoyed at a teacher who uses&nbsp;
his cup from the communal kitchen,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:10.240 --> 00:05:12.880
uncomfortable the woman&nbsp;
empties it and washes it out.

00:05:15.680 --> 00:05:20.800
He returns home to find Clare doing the puzzle,&nbsp;
he helps her and she takes the opportunity to&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:20.800 --> 00:05:25.440
stab the screwdriver through his hand resting&nbsp;
on the tabletop, pinning him to the table.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:25.440 --> 00:05:30.800
She grabs the keys and escapes down the stairwell&nbsp;
and across the courtyard, but a clunky door jams&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:30.800 --> 00:05:35.600
and Andi catches her and crushes her hand in the&nbsp;
door as she escapes through the front building,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:35.600 --> 00:05:39.520
breaking her finger. He carries a&nbsp;
passed out Clare back to the apartment.

00:05:41.840 --> 00:05:47.200
The following day he meets his father. When&nbsp;
he returns home Clare tries to return calmness&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:47.200 --> 00:05:52.240
to the hostile situation. She continues to&nbsp;
plead to him and tells him she misses her Mum&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:52.240 --> 00:05:56.560
but Andi tells her, there's no point missing&nbsp;
something you won't get back, and that she&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:56.560 --> 00:06:02.560
has him instead. Andi constantly takes photos of&nbsp;
Clare in odd and disturbed poses, usually naked.

00:06:04.960 --> 00:06:11.040
The next day Andi watches the female student,&nbsp;
Franka in gym class, aroused. Meanwhile,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:11.040 --> 00:06:15.920
Clare attempts to pick the door locks with a&nbsp;
paperclip, snapping one off in the internal door,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:15.920 --> 00:06:21.200
and worries Andi will discover her attempt. We see&nbsp;
that Andi has locked all the sharp tools in the&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:21.200 --> 00:06:26.720
lock-box with the key. He continues to taunt and&nbsp;
intimidate Clare both mentally and emotionally,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:26.720 --> 00:06:31.360
moving between affection, possessiveness&nbsp;
and cruelty. Andi is washing Clare in the&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:31.360 --> 00:06:36.320
shower when Franka knocks at the door. Andi&nbsp;
threatens Clare that if she says anything,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:36.320 --> 00:06:40.560
he will kill the girl. Andi answers&nbsp;
the door and Franka flirts with him,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:40.560 --> 00:06:44.880
stating she followed him home. Seeing&nbsp;
Clare standing in a towel in the hallway,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:44.880 --> 00:06:50.240
Andi tells her she's his girlfriend and is cruel&nbsp;
to her so she leaves. Back inside the apartment&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:50.240 --> 00:06:56.080
Clare enquires about the girl, asking her name,&nbsp;
and Andi cuts her hair, again photographing her.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:56.080 --> 00:07:00.129
Later he discovers the internal door&nbsp;
won't open and gets cross with Clare.

00:07:02.400 --> 00:07:07.680
We see time pass, it's now Christmas. Clare&nbsp;
is living in terror, but as Andi continues to&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:07.680 --> 00:07:13.200
toy with her she begins to unravel and act out,&nbsp;
Andi at one point asking her to be 'normal' and&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:13.200 --> 00:07:18.400
gets violent in his frustration at her behavior,&nbsp;
leaving to stay with his father. The power in the&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:18.400 --> 00:07:23.760
apartment goes out and Clare is stuck for days&nbsp;
without power. It's freezing cold and she eats&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:23.760 --> 00:07:29.520
the little food she finds. Andi's father dies and&nbsp;
upset, he waits a few days to call the caretaker,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:29.520 --> 00:07:34.800
remaining in his father's house. Clare finds&nbsp;
another girls toenail trimming under the bed.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:34.800 --> 00:07:38.720
Clare is relieved when Andi returns&nbsp;
to the apartment a few days later.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:38.720 --> 00:07:43.360
Andi was unaware of the power outage and&nbsp;
tells him "she thought he wasn't coming back".&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:43.360 --> 00:07:48.160
She comforts him about his father's passing and&nbsp;
they continue to have another meat injection game.

00:07:50.400 --> 00:07:55.600
Clare begins warming to the situation, cleaning,&nbsp;
cooking, making an effort with her appearance,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:55.600 --> 00:08:01.360
playing music. Andi gives her a book and his&nbsp;
father's dog for Christmas. Clare asks the details&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:01.360 --> 00:08:05.840
of why he chose her and he explains he saw her in&nbsp;
the street looking at the woman airing the sheet&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:05.840 --> 00:08:10.400
out the window, unveiling that he had planned&nbsp;
their meeting in the bookshop. Clare asks about&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:10.400 --> 00:08:15.440
the previous girl, and we see a sudden shift in&nbsp;
his affection for Clare, annoyed at her questions.

00:08:17.520 --> 00:08:23.200
Sometime later, he takes her from the apartment&nbsp;
into an isolated forest. He's carrying an axe.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:23.200 --> 00:08:28.640
While Clare appreciates being outside finally&nbsp;
he lifts his axe behind her. But a young boy&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:28.640 --> 00:08:33.600
shouts and runs over, interrupting, asking&nbsp;
to help his brother who has hurt his leg.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:33.600 --> 00:08:38.320
Surprised at their presence, Andi is&nbsp;
distracted and Clare seizes an opportunity&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:38.320 --> 00:08:42.960
to try to alert the other boy, but he doesn't&nbsp;
understand english and is frightened by her&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:42.960 --> 00:08:48.160
urgency. Andi notices and is angry at Clare.&nbsp;
When the mother collects her children,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:48.160 --> 00:08:53.440
Andi leads Clare back to the car and forces&nbsp;
her into the boot, returning to the apartment.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:53.440 --> 00:08:58.240
Andi now annoyed at Clare's presence and jealous&nbsp;
of her relationship with the dog, takes the dog&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:58.240 --> 00:09:03.840
for a walk and doesn't return with it, stating it&nbsp;
'ran away'. Clare is alone again and heartbroken.

00:09:06.400 --> 00:09:10.480
While Andi attends a New Year's Eve&nbsp;
party, Clare breaks into the locked room,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:10.480 --> 00:09:16.640
finding his camera, a massage chair, and a photo&nbsp;
album of Clare in captivity. Clare also finds an&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:16.640 --> 00:09:22.240
album of another girl, blonde, bound and abused&nbsp;
in the same way. Andi attempts to lure another&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:22.240 --> 00:09:27.360
young female tourist, sparking conversation and&nbsp;
using the same miss-wording he used with Clare,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:27.360 --> 00:09:32.240
confusing 'contemplate life' with 'compensate&nbsp;
life', but the girl leaves with her friend.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:32.240 --> 00:09:36.720
Back in the kitchen, Clare notices a torchlight&nbsp;
shining from another apartment across the&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:36.720 --> 00:09:42.080
courtyard and alerts the person to her distress,&nbsp;
screaming and smashing the repaired window pane.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:42.080 --> 00:09:46.240
A man reaches the apartment door&nbsp;
nearly freeing Clare, but Andi returns&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:46.240 --> 00:09:50.880
and kills him with a hammer. Andi taunts&nbsp;
Clare that it is her fault the man is dead&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:50.880 --> 00:09:55.930
and forces her to help wrap up the body which&nbsp;
he burns in the coal pit in courtyard outside.

00:09:58.160 --> 00:10:01.600
The following day Andi cleans the&nbsp;
blood and boards up the windows,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:10:01.600 --> 00:10:06.880
punishing Clare. He notices a missing persons&nbsp;
ad in the local paper, with Clare's picture and&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:10:06.880 --> 00:10:12.240
flustered asks Clare to pack her bags because&nbsp;
he is fumigating the apartment. Clare notices&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:10:12.240 --> 00:10:17.360
student workbooks on the table that Andi&nbsp;
is grading. She purposefully burns her hand&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:10:17.360 --> 00:10:22.089
and while Andi grabs some cream from the&nbsp;
bathroom, she stashes away Franka's workbook.

00:10:24.720 --> 00:10:29.680
The following morning Andi tips out all&nbsp;
the drinks and takes his and Clare's bags,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:10:29.680 --> 00:10:34.080
leaving Clare behind in the apartment.&nbsp;
Downstairs he stashes Clare's bag in&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:10:34.080 --> 00:10:39.680
the basement and turns off the pipes, leaving&nbsp;
Clare without water. At school he hands out the&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:10:39.680 --> 00:10:44.720
workbooks and Franka finds a photo of Clare&nbsp;
bound and gagged slipped between the pages.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:10:44.720 --> 00:10:49.360
Without drawing attention to her discovery,&nbsp;
Franka excuses herself from the classroom&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:10:49.360 --> 00:10:54.720
and flees promptly on her bike. The photo is found&nbsp;
on the floor by the other students and panicked,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:10:54.720 --> 00:11:00.560
Andi rushes back to the apartment, getting stuck&nbsp;
in traffic. Andi finds Franka's bike outside the&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:11:00.560 --> 00:11:05.760
front building and sees where she has broken in&nbsp;
through a basement window. He finds the hammer and&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:11:05.760 --> 00:11:11.120
the lock-box open in the courtyard, and a window&nbsp;
in the building block open. The apartment door is&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:11:11.120 --> 00:11:17.120
open and Clare is gone. He follows muddy footsteps&nbsp;
up the stairwell and we see him follow them past&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:11:17.120 --> 00:11:22.000
Clare hiding in a stairwell cupboard. Just as&nbsp;
he reaches the room where Franka is hiding,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:11:22.000 --> 00:11:27.600
Clare calls from downstairs, luring him back&nbsp;
into the apartment. Once he is distracted inside,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:11:27.600 --> 00:11:32.000
Clare manages to slip out and lock the&nbsp;
apartment door with Andi now trapped inside.

00:11:34.720 --> 00:11:39.200
A wave of euphoric relief washes over Clare&nbsp;
as she realizes she is finally free from&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:11:39.200 --> 00:11:43.840
the apartment and Andi. Andi now pleading&nbsp;
for Clare to free him from the apartment,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:11:43.840 --> 00:11:47.680
she screams in victory, chucking the&nbsp;
keys against the outside of the door,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:11:47.680 --> 00:11:53.360
taunting Andi. She collects Franka and has found&nbsp;
a bag with her passport and her mother's ring.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:11:53.360 --> 00:11:57.520
The final shots are of Andi relaxing in&nbsp;
his massage chair and Clare riding in a&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:11:57.520 --> 00:12:01.505
